    title: "Finding the Best Dentist in Tucson, Arizona",
    description: "From the Catalina Foothills and Sam Hughes to Marana, Sahuarita, and the Oro Valley — a guide to dental care across Pima County for patients at every stage of life.",
    author: "Dr. Sarah Mitchell, DDS",
